tell on sight that a person has been drinking or using other drugs, the person is<br />
visibly intoxicated.</p>

<p>If a person shows a combination of several signs that could be a strong indication that the person is intoxicated. Remember that intoxication can result from the use of drugs other than alcohol.</p>

